com.mambu.apisdk.model
Class LoanAccountExpanded

java.lang.Object
  com.mambu.apisdk.model.LoanAccountExpanded

public class LoanAccountExpanded
extends java.lang.Object

A class which expands the definition of the Mambu's LoanAccount to include custom fields in the format expected by the Mambu's createLoanAccount() Json API. The primary purpose of this class to supply LoanAccount and custom information in the format expected by this API and which can be automaticlaly parsed by Gson to/from json. Example of the expected json format for creating LoanAccount (Mambu 3.2) {"loanAccount":{.....}, "customInformation":[{field1},{field2}]} The class provides just basic getters and setters loanAccount and customInformation. It's primary purpose is to represent a Json object for LoanAccount creation API.

Author:
mdanilkis
